(11, 1, '2025-05-05 17:21:58', '2025-05-05 17:21:58', '<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"304\">Our Mission</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"305\" data-end=\"592\">At ScribbleNews, we believe in the power of storytelling. Our mission is to deliver insightful, creative, and thought-provoking content that goes beyond the headlines. Whether it’s breaking news, in-depth features, or artistic explorations, we are here to keep you informed and inspired.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"594\" data-end=\"610\">Who We Are</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"611\" data-end=\"882\">ScribbleNews is a dynamic team of writers, journalists, and creatives who are passionate about uncovering stories that matter. With backgrounds in journalism, art, literature, and digital media, we bring a diverse set of voices and perspectives to every piece we publish.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"903\">What We Cover</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"1188\">From world affairs and cultural movements to emerging artists and underground trends, our content reflects the rich tapestry of the modern world. We shine a light on the intersections between news and creativity—because we know that art, politics, and people are all deeply connected.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1190\" data-end=\"1213\">Why ScribbleNews?</h3>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1214\" data-end=\"1427\">The name “ScribbleNews” reflects our belief that every great story starts with a scribble—a spark of curiosity, a sketch of an idea, a note jotted in the margin. We turn those scribbles into stories that resonate.</p>\r\n<p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-21ogod\" data-styles-preset=\"xZndidUCt\">Team Scribble</p>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2025-05-06 06:53:22', '2025-05-06 06:53:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/scribblenews/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
